0 -15 Td
(economy states. The baseline policy used conventional double-smoke commits without staged timing) Tj
0 -15 Td
(offsets. Compared with baseline, the triple-smoke protocol improved successful site entry rate,) Tj
0 -15 Td
(reduced first-five-second post-plant deaths, and increased round conversion in medium-) Tj
