0 -15 Td
(For ranked application, players should first memorize two safe fallback routes per site pair and) Tj
0 -15 Td
(pre-assign smoke ownership before buy phase ends. During execution, teams should avoid) Tj
0 -15 Td
(collapsing all smokes into one burst unless defending utility is already exhausted. If the first) Tj
0 -15 Td
(contact fails and utility parity is lost, the recommended policy is FREEZE and regroup rather) Tj
0 -15 Td
(than forced late entry. This converts chaotic rounds into recoverable setups.) Tj
